**  ER (ERROR MESSAGE)
E-01 SELECT NO IS <1 OR 2>
E-02 OUTPUT ORDER IS <1 OR 2>
E-03 NOT INPUT INTRAL COMPANY PART NUMBER
E-04 THERE IS NO INTRAL PART NUMBER IN DIE ALLOTMENT M/F
E-05 THIS INTRAL PART NUMBER IS FIN TO BE OUTPUT LISTS
E-06 THIS PROCESS IS NOT IN PROCESS NAME M/F
E-07 THIS DEPARTMENT IS NOT IN DETAIL M/F
E-08 MACHINE NUMBER IS NOT IN MACHINE ABILITY M/F BY DEPART
E-09 IT ALREADY FINISHED TO BE OUTPUT LIST
E-10 YOU HAVE TO EXIT BECAUSE YOU CAN NOT INPUT
E-11 YOU HAVE TO INPUT PROCESS, DEPARTMENT AND MACHINE NBR
E-12 MUST INPUT<6>FOR FACTORY NUMBER
E-13 DIE ALLOTMENT MASTER FILE IS NO DATA.
